Description: Integrated Subversion support for Nautilus
 An extension to Nautilus to allow better integration with the Subversion source
 control system. NautilusSVN adds Subversion related commands to the Nautilus
 context menu, and Subversion-controlled directories will be detected
 automatically and decorated with appropriate emblems. It is similar to the
 TortoiseSVN project on Windows.
